title: Our Awkward Moments From The 53rd Annual CMA Awards + Fast Food Items Draft + Amy’s Husband Recovering After Face Surgery
itunes:title: Our Awkward Moments From The 53rd Annual CMA Awards + Fast Food Items Draft + Amy’s Husband Recovering After Face Surgery
description:
We talk all about the CMA Awards last night. Bobby presented with Joe Walsh from the Eagles. Plus, we all had really awkward moments from the night and we vote on who was the most awkward. We do our Fast Food Items draft and Amy gives us an update on her husband's surgery for melanoma.
